- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses the deployment and maintenance of broadband networks, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society): The paper focuses on the role of BuB in developing the information society, which is a topic related to the intersection of computers and society. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper discusses the deployment of broadband networks, which involves the transmission and processing of information. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper discusses the participation of beneficiaries in the planning and deployment of broadband networks, which is a topic related to social and information networks. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): Although not a major focus of the paper, the deployment of broadband networks may involve security and privacy concerns, which falls under the scope of cryptography and security.
